Create a virtualenv with :

    python3.7 -m venv .venv

Activate it with :

    source .venv/bin/activate

Install dependecies with :

    pip3 --require-virtualenv install -U pip setuptools wheel
    pip3 --require-virtualenv install -r requirements.txt

Streamlit config is in .streamlit/config.toml
18080 will be forward to 2268

    [browser]
    gatherUsageStats = false

    [server]
    address="localhost"
    port=18080


Run streamlit app with :

    streamlit run Home.py
